Describe Regression tests for issue #41

    Before each
        call autopairs#Variables#_InitVariables()
        new | only!
    End
    It shouldn't be dumb with single quotes
        normal i 'foo
        call Expect("").CheckBuff(" 'foo'")
        normal 0i'
        call Expect("").CheckBuff("'' 'foo'")
    End
    It shouldn't be dumb with double quotes
        normal i "foo
        call Expect("").CheckBuff(' "foo"')
        normal 0i"
        call Expect("").CheckBuff('"" "foo"')
    End
    It should work in markdown
        new file.md | only!

        normal i 'foo
        call Expect("").CheckBuff(" 'foo'")
        normal a '
        call Expect("").CheckBuff(" 'foo '")
        normal 0i'
        call Expect("").CheckBuff("'' 'foo '")

        call Expect('"""').ToMatch('""""""')
        call Expect("```").ToMatch('``````')

        %d
    End
End
